Developer Terms of Use
des:
• How much do we know about our dreams? 
• Are they significant? 
• Do they affect our waking lives? 
• And, above all, what do they mean? 

iDream is the all-in-one skill to help you decode your dreams. We have thousands of dream meanings from abandonment to zebra. Every type of dream is covered with this skill.

Try out iDream today and discover what your dreams mean.

To Enable the Skill: 
- Search for "iDream" in the Alexa mobile app or at Amazon.com and look for "iDream - Dream Dictionary and Dream Interpreter"

- Click the enable button on the Dream Dictionary skill page.

- To Get Started: Say "Alexa, open Dream Dictionary".

- You can now ask the iDream questions like, "I had a dream about {subject}", "What is the meaning of {subject} 

We would love to hear from you! If you have questions, comments, or feedback, please e-mail us at support@digitalmovement.co.uk.
